<item>
            <title>[PIG-2761] With hadoop23 importing modules inside python script does not work</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2761</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Because unjar has been removed from 23, registering scripts has issue. &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2745&quot; title=&quot;Pig e2e test RubyUDFs fails in MR mode when running from tarball&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-2745&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-2745&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; addresses the issue of registering scripts with pig. But if the registered py script imports other modules then it does not work. Steps to reproduce the issue in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2745?focusedCommentId=13396965&amp;amp;page=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.issuetabpanels:comment-tabpanel#comment-13396965&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2745?focusedCommentId=13396965&amp;amp;page=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.issuetabpanels:comment-tabpanel#comment-13396965&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12595165">PIG-2761</key>
            <summary>With hadoop23 importing modules inside python script does not work</summary>
